view.name: Food Resources in California
view.description: This dataset contains a list of resources such food pantries, food banks, and other food distribution sites throughout the state of California. The data is current as of May 1, 2020. Due to the coronavirus pandemic, many food pantries may change their hours or close temporarily. Please contact a food pantry prior to visiting them to confirm their operating hours and ensure you are in their service area.
